+++ openpatch_agent_gateway_v11_candidate/README.md	2026-05-06 01:37:51.204585821 +0000
@@ -34,3 +34,8 @@
 ## v10 update
 
 Adds route visual map, route fix suggestions, route-resolution stress API/CLI, and `openpatch.agent_button.v10` marker with `routeVisualHint`. This is intended to prevent wrong repo/key/project routing across many pages, browsers, and agents.
+
+
+## V11 update
+
+V11 adds real-smoke readiness APIs: `/config-lint`, `/smoke/plan`, `/instances`, and CLI commands for Codex-friendly bridge-only smoke. It also upgrades button markers to `openpatch.agent_button.v11` with smoke/bridge instance hints.
diff -ruN openpatch_agent_gateway_v10_candidate/auto-continue-integration/AUTO_CONTINUE_LIVE_ADAPTER_V11.md openpatch_agent_gateway_v11_candidate/auto-continue-integration/AUTO_CONTINUE_LIVE_ADAPTER_V11.md
--- openpatch_agent_gateway_v10_candidate/auto-continue-integration/AUTO_CONTINUE_LIVE_ADAPTER_V11.md	1970-01-01 00:00:00.000000000 +0000
+++ openpatch_agent_gateway_v11_candidate/auto-continue-integration/AUTO_CONTINUE_LIVE_ADAPTER_V11.md	2026-05-06 01:37:51.204444374 +0000
@@ -0,0 +1,12 @@
+# Auto Continue Live Adapter V11
+
+Integrate as a small adapter, not a hard merge.
+
+Auto Continue should:
+- Ask bridge `/agent/compact-summary` before continuing.
+- Ask `/smoke/plan` or `/auto-continue/plan` when a roundpack is due.
+- Send RoundPack prompt and wait for `[ROUND_PACK_READY]`.
+- Listen for OpenPatch receipt/status event.
+- Continue only after receipt or clear retry/failure state.
+
+Auto Continue should not store GitHub tokens.
